Workspace Rules for Mitzi's Website
File Access
When asked to read or analyze a .docx file, always use the installed Python environment.

Use the command: py -m pip show python-docx to verify the library if needed.

Execute reading tasks via: py -c "import docx; doc = docx.Document('FILENAME.docx'); [print(p.text) for p in doc.paragraphs if p.text.strip()]"

Environment Context
Operating System: Windows (PowerShell)

Primary Python Command: py

Project Goal: Local SEO and Keyword Optimization for Mitzi Santayana (Realtor).